---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1 class="hero-h1"><span>Security control plane</span> for MCP and agent tool access</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Govern identity, policy, discovery, and audit with an MCP-native gateway that enforces every tool invocation before execution.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="#install" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/vellaveto/vellaveto" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View on GitHub</a>
    </div>
    <p class="trust-strip">MCP-native gateway &middot; topology inventory &middot; identity-aware policy &middot; 9,000+ tests</p>
    <div class="install" id="install">
      <span class="label">Quick start</span>
      <code>docker run -p 3000:3000 ghcr.io/vellaveto/vellaveto:latest</code>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero{padding:9rem 0 5rem;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 20% 20%,rgba(167,139,250,.15),transparent),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 80%,rgba(20,184,166,.12),transparent);
    pointer-events:none}
  .hero::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
    background-image:radial-gradient(circle 1px at center,rgba(255,255,255,.03) 1px,transparent 1px);
    background-size:40px 40px;pointer-events:none}
  .hero .wrap{position:relative;z-index:1}
  .hero-h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:800;
    line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:1rem;
    animation:fadeInUp .6s ease both}
  .hero-h1 span{background:var(--grad);-webkit-background-clip:text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
  .tagline{font-size:1.125rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;
    max-width:600px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;
    animation:fadeInUp .6s ease .1s both}
  .hero-ctas{display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1.5rem;
    animation:fadeInUp .6s ease .2s both}
  .trust-strip{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:2.5rem;
    animation:fadeInUp .6s ease .3s both}
  .install{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:.5rem;padding:1rem 1.25rem;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.875rem;overflow-x:auto;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);
    animation:fadeInUp .6s ease .4s both}
  .install code{white-space:nowrap;color:var(--accent)}
  .label{color:var(--muted);font-size:.75rem;font-family:var(--sans);flex-shrink:0}
  @media(max-width:600px){
    .hero{padding:7rem 0 3.5rem}
    .hero-h1{font-size:1.75rem}
    .install{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}
    .hero-ctas{flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
  }
</style>
